{"id":"the-mountain-echo","slug":"the-mountain-echo","title":"The Mountain Echo","title_ko":"산울림","level":"A2","ageBand":"8-10","coverUrl":"/seed/the-mountain-echo/cover.webp","summary_ko":"산에서 메아리를 처음 들은 아이가 그 신비를 알아가는 하루.","wordCount":175,"pages":[{"id":"the-mountain-echo-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-mountain-echo/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-mountain-echo-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"One bright morning, Mina walked up the green mountain.","translation_ko":"어느 맑은 아침, 미나는 푸른 산을 올랐어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-mountain-echo/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"One","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":280},{"word":"bright","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":280,"endMs":520},{"word":"morning","charStart":11,"charEnd":18,"startMs":520,"endMs":900},{"word":"Mina","charStart":20,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1320,"endMs":1520},{"word":"walked","charStart":25,"charEnd":31,"startMs":1520,"endMs":1880},{"word":"up","charStart":32,"charEnd":34,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2100},{"word":"the","charStart":35,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2100,"endMs":2320},{"word":"green","charStart":39,"charEnd":44,"startMs":2320,"endMs":2560},{"word":"mountain","charStart":45,"charEnd":53,"startMs":2560,"endMs":2820}]},{"id":"the-mountain-echo-p1-s2","ord":1,"text":"Her red backpack was full of snacks and water.","translation_ko":"빨간 가방에는 간식과 물이 가득 들어 있었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-mountain-echo/audio/p1-s2.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Her","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":420},{"word":"red","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":420,"endMs":880},{"word":"backpack","charStart":8,"charEnd":16,"startMs":880,"endMs":1400},{"word":"was","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1400,"endMs":1840},{"word":"full","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":1840,"endMs":2040},{"word":"of","charStart":26,"charEnd":28,"startMs":2040,"endMs":2580},{"word":"snacks","charStart":29,"charEnd":35,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2580},{"word":"and","charStart":36,"charEnd":39,"startMs":2580,"endMs":2940},